{"tid":496701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為了強制員工下班 日本搞了一架無人機","createTime":"2017-12-12T03:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T15:06:26.000Z","uid":141060,"like":339,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"52c029354475bea2e51c7a5e9da749c6698f46b8","tid":496701,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"日本人加班是出了名的，官方數據顯示，日本人平均一年（8760個小時）的工作時間累計超過2000個小時，每年至少有200人死於過勞死，由過勞死引發的索賠案件逐年增加。<br />\n最近，一家叫Taisei的公司為了讓員工不加班，聯合無人機制造商Blue Innovation和電信公司NTT East推出了一架能強迫員工離開辦公室的無人機。<br />\n方式也很簡單粗暴，如果員工想加班，無人機就會在旁邊放歌兒干擾他們，讓他們無心工作。<br />\n有意思的是，無人機播放的那首曲子還是聞名世界的《友誼地久天長》，官方表示，日本很多商店打烊的時候都會播放這首歌。<br />\nT-Frend也在考慮在無人機上增加面部識別功能，這樣就能分辨誰還在公司加班。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/111133_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F111133_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=9bedfb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d2099b4b4fa835c297f327717566b6cd725549","tid":496701,"uid":2404,"like":996,"dislike":3,"score":993,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"絕不下班的員工 vs 絕對要趕走員工的無人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a7ecdb2a9a2d8c862df3ecf4f2415eced91a70","tid":496701,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"播兒歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6630f85b10b0b2ae8ca611a73cbae3b5a9cfbd3e","tid":496701,"uid":79563,"like":281,"dislike":2,"score":279,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕不下班的員工 vs 絕對要趕走員工的無人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5ZvWKsa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5ZvWKsa.png&h=dbde