if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：平均都起碼9個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f816709ac7184db5b9a8da3c108b05bd058c31cb","tid":496701,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"計下自已重慘高日本仔..."},{"pid":"2a44ede490ca121b46b381478e724b819f180916","tid":496701,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"其實過2000個鐘都好正常"},{"pid":"68ab60bf672066f2a6557717d67eeb05ef05b510","tid":496701,"uid":28549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計下自已重慘高日本仔...</blockquote><br />\n日本仔打左卡會返埋位繼續做野<br />\nD數字都係呃鴺人<br />\n因為勞工條例限左個ot上限<br />\n打卡當收左工算係走法律隙<br />\n特別d新入職, 之前做到死個日本妹好似話經常兩三日無得返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553cec604d7c36fdd64e586f21b2e6db5c261c7b","tid":496701,"uid":13010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>播兒歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n播歌兒 丫，大陸垃圾兒化音"},{"pid":"38c700f002d52e309f5a6cf64d2c1a66efa38dec","tid":496701,"uid":135866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意返工"},{"pid":"73c49a720ffc84baee32dc190a3b8f84800d91b5","tid":496701,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"早啲放工一齊陪老闆去飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48141db9598ca45cbde7a6bd20b6942314e1e7fa","tid":496701,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8小時+正常1小時OT，24日，12個月<br />\n都2592小時，如果咁計，香港點都多過佢喎<br />\n<br />\n日本人平均做3000小時炸掛，換算番姐係每日番10個鐘多啲，再放工應酬，咁就好似差不多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/162042_f22c6f9a2f8051b123e36d195cb5deee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht